ActCanada Deposit Insurance Corporation Act
SubjectCanada Deposit Insurance Corporation (CDIC) ** Maximum annual premium **
PrecisOrder fixing the percentage used respecting the maximum CANADA DEPOSIT INSURANCE annual membership PREMIUM RATE at twenty-eight one hundredths of one per cent (or 28 basis points of insured deposits) for the premium year beginning on May 1, 2014 and ending on April 30, 2015.
